data.description: Back on Market at No Fault of Seller! This beautiful 4 bedroom 2 bath home sits quietly nestled in the center of Fort Walton Beach! Completely renovated in 2021! Open floor plan with a primary suite and two walk-in closets! The living area opens up to the kitchen making it perfect for entertaining. New cabinets, Granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a sizable island with cooktop, and a desk area all installed in 2021. LVP flooring in main areas, remodeled bathrooms, Energy Efficient Windows, 2020 HVAC, Water Heater, and Roof! The spacious screened in patio is the ideal place to unwind while overlooking the expansive backyard! Military bases, shopping, schools, recreational areas, and the beach are all conveniently nearby. New Sprinkler System installed in 2021
